response.overview: Jigsaw has disappeared. Along with his new apprentice Amanda, the puppet-master behind the cruel, intricate games that have terrified a community and baffled police has once again eluded capture and vanished. While city detective scrambles to locate him, Doctor Lynn Denlon and Jeff Reinhart are unaware that they are about to become the latest pawns on his vicious chessboard.
response.tagline: Suffering? You haven't seen anything yet...
response.title: Saw III

titles.title: SAW III - Hast Du das Leben verdient?
